snippet.title: Demo Trailer - KILL THE WITCH
snippet.description:
" So I came to smash everything. 
Not to leave a single piece of dust behind. "
 
The time when humans gave up being happy to be no longer unhappy and became 'bugs'.
The story of a witch who smashes everything with a baseball bat tightly in her hand.
